2019-06-11  Richard Frith-Macdonald <rfm@gnu.org>

	* Headers/GNUstepBase/GSIArray.h:
	* Headers/GNUstepBase/NSObject+GNUstepBase.h:
	* Source/Additions/NSObject+GNUstepBase.m:
	* Source/GSArray.m:
	* Source/GSCountedSet.m:
	* Source/GSDictionary.m:
	* Source/GSSet.m:
