	recursive interactions with tracking NSL:ock activity.

2018-03-27  Richard Frith-Macdonald <rfm@gnu.org>

	* Source/GSPrivate.h:
	* Source/NSDebug.m:
	* Source/NSException.m:
	* Source/NSThread.m:
	* Headers/Foundation/NSThread.h:
