	* Tools/AGSParser.m,
	* Tools/HTMLLinker.m,
	* Tools/gspath.m
	* Tools/pl.m:
	Replace all -release messages sent to autorelease pools with -drain. In
	non-GC mode, these are equivalent.
	In GC mode, these trigger a collection.

