2010-07-26  Nicola Pero  <nicola.pero@meta-innovation.com>

	* Documentation/GNUmakefile (REF_DOC_INSTALL_DIR): Use
	GNUSTEP_DOC, not GNUSTEP_DOCUMENTATION, which has been deprecated
	for over 3 years.
