2006-03-24  Richard Frith-Macdonald <rfm@gnu.org>

	* Source/GSRunLoopCtxt.h:
	* Source/unix/GSRunLoopCtxt.m:
	* Source/win32/GSRunLoopCtxt.m:
	Tidy/improve removal of triggered watchers from outer contexts.
